Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.09,0:00:07.21,Default,Gamma,0,0,0,,哼哼哼～
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.21,0:00:09.20,Default,Alpha,0,0,0,,这是…巧克力？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.20,0:00:14.72,Default,Gamma,0,0,0,,哼哼哼～ 并不只是普通的巧克力啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.72,0:00:16.75,Default,Gamma,0,0,0,,其实这里面有威士忌
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.31,0:00:18.31,Default,Alpha,0,0,0,,威士忌…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.31,0:00:22.72,Default,Gamma,0,0,0,,是暗影大人教授的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.72,0:00:26.51,Default,Gamma,0,0,0,,将谷物蒸馏后存入木桶放置数年
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.51,0:00:28.29,Default,Gamma,0,0,0,,制作而成的黄金色美酒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.29,0:00:31.93,Default,Alpha,0,0,0,,数年…需要很花时间吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.93,0:00:35.01,Default,Gamma,0,0,0,,是的 但是这个顾虑已经…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.48,0:00:38.40,Default,Gamma,0,0,0,,被希妲完美解决了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.40,0:00:39.44,Default,Eta,0,0,0,,Ｖ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.44,0:00:45.74,Default,Gamma,0,0,0,,只要有了这套装置 便可以短时间制作大量威士忌了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.31,0:00:47.20,Default,Alpha,0,0,0,,好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.02,0:00:50.74,Default,Alpha,0,0,0,,但是为什么要把威士忌包裹入巧克力内
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.15,0:00:55.57,Default,Eta,0,0,0,,Master说 威士忌和巧克力很搭
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.57,0:01:00.25,Default,Gamma,0,0,0,,特意制成可以含入口中的量更美味
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.25,0:01:02.94,Default,Gamma,0,0,0,,所以就将威士忌包裹了起来
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.94,0:01:05.54,Default,Alpha,0,0,0,,欸～好主意啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.54,0:01:09.78,Default,Gamma,0,0,0,,虽然不知是否达成了暗影大人所描绘的目标
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.78,0:01:14.60,Default,Gamma,0,0,0,,但想将其作为下期三越商会新产品发售
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.02,0:01:18.42,Default,Alpha,0,0,0,,我觉得不错 那么名称有了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.42,0:01:22.23,Default,Gamma,0,0,0,,啊 说起来还没决定呢 叫什么好呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.47,0:01:25.92,Default,Alpha,0,0,0,,边吃边决定吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.92,0:01:26.97,Default,Gamma,0,0,0,,也是…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.97,0:01:27.82,Default,Eta,0,0,0,,吃…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.71,0:01:33.92,Default,Gamma,0,0,0,,希妲…我不行了…这个…酒…很烈…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.28,0:01:36.97,Default,Alpha,0,0,0,,伽玛很容易醉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.97,0:01:38.14,Default,Gamma,0,0,0,,欸…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.42,0:01:42.80,Default,Gamma,0,0,0,,脑袋感觉飘飘的…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.39,0:01:44.81,Default,Alpha,0,0,0,,不是涨涨的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.17,0:01:49.57,Default,Eta,0,0,0,,名称决定了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.57,0:01:50.26,Default,Gamma,0,0,0,,欸！？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.95,0:01:53.92,Default,Eta,0,0,0,,命名“威士忌飘飘”
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.56,0:01:57.42,Default,Alpha,0,0,0,,威士忌飘飘…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.03,0:01:59.73,Default,Alpha,0,0,0,,会不会有些难念？
